1) Install Mac OS X El Capitan Version 10.11.6

2) Install Homebrew from http://brew.sh

3) Run as follows.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
$ brew install clutter-gst gstreamer gst-plugins-good gst-plugins-bad gst-plugins-ugly gst-libav
$ git clone https://bitbucket.org/ohhara/ohmultivideoplayer.git
$ cd ohmultivideoplayer
$ ./configure
$ make
$ ./omvp
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
